__Please read all the rules carefully!__

:one: We cannot mention every rule we expect you to abide by and for this reason we ask you use common sense. If we deem your behavior a violation of our rules we will have to take action on your account.

:two: We do not permit discriminatory speech, content, or actions based on race or ethnic origin, national origin, religion or religious affiliation, gender, gender identity, or sexual orientation.

:three: Do not organize, participate in, or encourage hateful conduct/harassment of others. We will not tolerate this behavior and we will take action against all users involved.

:four: No spamming in text channels. This includes but not limited to, Typing separate lines very quickly, Typing out large blocks of text, Flash Posting Invite links etc.

:five: Do not attempt to bypass the chat filters. Doing so will result in moderation action against your account.

:six: No suspicious links. Usage of IP Grabbers, Malware, or Cookie Stealing software is considered Exploiting and you will be banned immediately

:seven: Joining the server with the hostile intention to Raid, "nuke", grief or other damaging behaviors will lead to an automatic ban.

:eight: Attempting to use alt accounts to engage in any kind of punishment evasion or rule breaking behavior will lead you to an automatic ban.

:nine: Respect the channel topic assigned for each channel. 

:keycap_ten: Abuse of our server bots is prohibited and will result in a revoke of your permission to use them.


__***Disclaimer:***__

:warning: We reserve the right to blacklist at anytime for any reason regardless if it isn't listed above.

:exclamation: If you reach 3 verbal warnings you will be muted, if you reach 5 verbal warnings you will be kicked.

:1234: Warnings are accumulative.
